Program: Omnibus
Title: Art Spiegelman
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jsc
Last Broadcast Date: 01 February 1990
Art Spiegelman is an American comics artist, advocate for the medium of comics and founder of avant-garde comic 'Raw'. Here he talks about his graphic novel memoir, 'Maus' about his father's experiences as a Polish Jew and Holocaust survivor